article_title: Seth Meyers FINALLY Puts Elizabeth Warren Presidential Run Talk To Rest
article_text:
Well which is it, senator?!

With wishy-washy responses like, "No, I'm not running for president" and "No, I won't run," it's difficult to really know if Sen. Elizabeth Warren is or isn't running for president. MAKE UP YOUR MIND.

"Late Night with Seth Meyers" takes Warren to task for consistently dodging the question in their segment "Will They Or Won't They."

"Is Elizabeth Warren from Belgium, because she sure likes to ... WAFFLE."

"Late night with Seth Meyers" airs weeknights at 12:35EST on NBC.
